  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Wing Over is an arcade flight sim released for the PS1 in 1997. Featuring system link support for multi-player and a full single player tournament system, as well as a large roster of characters and planes to choose from, Wing Over has earned the title of a cult classic on the PS1.",
